== Spanish ==
=== Etymology ===
From ''[[cualquiera]]''
=== Adjective ===
'''cualquier''' ''m'' ''f'' (''pl'': '''cualesquier''')
# [[any]]; [[whatever]]; [[whichever]]

=== Usage note ===
Used before a noun, as in ''cualquier cosa''.  If it appears after a noun, it would take a form such as ''una cosa [[cualquiera]]''
